  (function () {
    var noop = function noop() {};
    if ("performance" in window === false) {
      window.performance = {};
    }
    window.performance.mark = performance.mark || noop;
    window.performance.measure = performance.measure || noop;
    if ("now" in window.performance === false) {
      var nowOffset = Date.now();
      if (performance.timing && performance.timing.navigationStart) {
        nowOffset = performance.timing.navigationStart;
      }
      window.performance.now = function now() {
        return Date.now() - nowOffset;
      };
    }
  })();

<script id="wix-first-paint">
    if (window.ResizeObserver &&
        (!window.PerformanceObserver || !PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes || PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes.indexOf('paint') === -1)) {
        new ResizeObserver(function (entries, observer) {
            entries.some(function (entry) {
                var contentRect = entry.contentRect;
                if (contentRect.width > 0 && contentRect.height > 0) {
                    requestAnimationFrame(function (now) {
                        window.wixFirstPaint = now;
                        dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('wixFirstPaint'));
                    });
                    observer.disconnect();
                    return true;
                }
            });
        }).observe(document.body);
    }
</script>

    </g>
</svg>
</div></span></div></a></div><div id="comp-kp6rr375" class="c9GqVL QxJLC3 comp-kp6rr375 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="text-decoration:underline;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><a href="mailto:connect@pcs.org.sg" target="_self" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Please email completed Employment Application Form to connect@pcs.org.sg.</span></a></span></p></div><div id="comp-kofsmrti" class="c9GqVL QxJLC3 comp-kofsmrti wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h1 class="font_0 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:50px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Childcare Teacher</span></h1>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">The Childcare Teacher will be responsible for creating a quality learning environment and a secure environment for children. She will work with team members to co-design the curriculum together with the in-house Curriculum Specialist, and will integrate innovative teaching &amp; learning practices in her implementation of the curriculum. Most importantly, she will embrace and cultivate values that will prepare children at the centre to be lifelong learners and contributing members of the society.</span></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">​</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">The Childcare Teacher will partner parents &amp; the community to foster children’s holistic development.</span></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Teachers will be provided with basic training to work with children with mild developmental needs. For those who are keen to work more closely with children with special needs, opportunities are available for them to undergo additional training to become Learning Support Educators (LSEd).</span></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">​</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_3a4612c531d149e89813dc52a679f440,wf_3a4612c531d149e89813dc52a,orig_glacialindifferencebold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Requirements</span></span></p>

<ul class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px;">
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Diploma or Certificate in Early Childhood Care and Education – Teaching (DECCE-T or CECCCE)</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Good communication and interpersonal skills</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">A team player</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Experience in the Early Childhood is an added advantage</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">We offer leadership mentoring, scholarship, lateral &amp; vertical career progression, attractive benefits and remuneration.</span></p>
</li>
</ul>

<h1 class="font_0 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:50px;">&nbsp;</h1>

<h1 class="font_0 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:50px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Infant Care Teacher</span></h1>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">The Infant Care Teacher supports the learning and development of infants and toddlers through interactive and stimulating experiences. She will partner with parents to foster the holistic development of infants and toddlers under her care. Some of the key responsibilities include:</span></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">​</span></span></span></p>

<ol class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px;">
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Provide quality, nurturing care to infants and toddlers enrolled in the programme</span></span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Communicate effectively with infants, toddlers, their parents and other staff</span></span></p>
</li>
</ol>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_3a4612c531d149e89813dc52a679f440,wf_3a4612c531d149e89813dc52a,orig_glacialindifferencebold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Requirements</span></span></span></p>

<ul class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px;">
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Certificate in Infant/Toddler Care &amp; Development (CIT) / Higher Certificate in Infant Care (HCIC)/</span></span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Advanced Certificate in Early Years (ACEY)</span></span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Candidates who are currently undergoing HCIC/ACEY are welcome to apply too</span></span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Preferably with relevant experience in teaching infant and toddlers</span></span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Singaporean or PR preferred</span></span></p>
</li>
</ul>

<h1 class="font_0 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:50px;">&nbsp;</h1>

<h1 class="font_0 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:50px;">Educational Support Teacher</h1>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">The Educational Support Teacher’s (EST) primary role is to support class teachers and children with developmental concerns/ special needs in the implementation of appropriate educational programming within an inclusive learning environment to ensure that each child’s potential is maximised. In addition, they also work closely with families and caregivers, early intervention professionals to support the delivery of programme and services.</span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Requirements</span></p>

<ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular; font-size:20px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Specialist Diploma in Early Childhood Intervention (Special Needs) (SDESN)</span></span></p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Proficient in written and spoken English</span></span></p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Strong multi-tasking skill</span></span></p>
</li>
</ul>

<h1 class="font_0 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:50px; line-height:normal;"><span style="font-size:50px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">​</span></span></h1>

<h1 class="font_0 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:50px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Learning Support Educator</span></h1>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">The Learning Support Educator (LSEd) is a key player to the success of the Development Support and Learning Support (DS-LS) Programme. A preschool teacher by training, the LSEd serves as a resource in the early childhood landscape by supporting preschool teachers and children with learning and developmental needs within the classroom setting. Some of the key responsibilities include:</span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;">&nbsp;</p>

<ol class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px;">
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Use prescribed screening tools to screen children referred by preschool teachers for learning and developmental issues</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Present screening outcomes to Paediatricians and the therapy teams at Case Filter Meetings</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Work collaboratively with teachers, therapists, caregivers and DS-LS professionals to provide support for children with mild developmental needs</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Work out the individual education plan (IEP) for the DS-LS children</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Support therapy teams by embedding the therapy goals into the classroom curriculum</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Conduct intervention through support packages to DS-LS children</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Provide in-class support to children who have received intervention packages</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Ensure goals set are achieved during sessions with the DS-LS children and are generalised into the classroom</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Complete End-of-Intervention (EOI) report at closure of case</span></p>
</li>
</ol>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_3a4612c531d149e89813dc52a679f440,wf_3a4612c531d149e89813dc52a,orig_glacialindifferencebold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Requirements</span></span></p>

<ul class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px;">
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Degree or Diploma in Early Childhood Education</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">At least 2 years of working experience in the related field is required for this position</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Specialist Diploma in Early Childhood Learning Support (SDELS) preferred</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Experience in EIPIC or Special Education setting an added advantage</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Possess excellent interpersonal skills</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Must have initiative and ability to work independently and yet be a good team player</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">An organised and systematic worker</span></p>
</li>
<li style="line-height:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Singaporean or PR preferred</span></p>
</li>
</ul></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></main><div id="soapAfterPagesContainer" class="page-without-sosp page-without-sosp"><div data-mesh-id="soapAfterPagesContainerinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="soapAfterPagesContainerinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><div id="CONTROLLER_COMP_CUSTOM_ID" style="display:none"></div><section id="comp-kzrd93ns" class="comp-kzrd93ns CohWsy wixui-column-strip"><div id="bgLayers_comp-kzrd93ns" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER" class="if7Vw2"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="tcElKx i1tH8h"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-kzrd93ns" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA" class="wG8dni"></div></div><div data-testid="columns" class="V5AUxf"><div id="comp-kzrd93pa" class="comp-kzrd93pa YzqVVZ wixui-column-strip__column"><div id="bgLayers_comp-kzrd93pa" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER" class="MW5IWV" style="opacity: 0; <p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:15px; line-height:2em;"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:15px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="text-decoration:underline;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><a href="https://www.presbypreschool.edu.sg/archive2023about" target="_blank" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">ABOUT US</span></span></a></span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:15px; line-height:2em;"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:15px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="text-decoration:underline;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><a href="https://www.presbypreschool.edu.sg/programme" target="_blank" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">PROGRAMMES</span></span></a></span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:15px; line-height:2em;"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:15px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="text-decoration:underline;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><a href="https://www.presbypreschool.edu.sg/centres" target="_blank" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">OUR CENTRES</span></span></a></span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:15px; line-height:2em;"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:15px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="text-decoration:underline;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><a href="https://www.presbypreschool.edu.sg/news" target="_blank" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">NEWS</span></span></a></span></span></span></p>
